{
    "publish_date": "2012-10-24T18:57:10.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT7M24S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: Welcome to my home\nmovie of the new McLaren", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "12.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "12C Spider.", 
            "dur": "1.185", 
            "start": "15.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It costs 195,500 pounds, which\nis 19 and 1/2 thousand more", 
            "dur": "5.145", 
            "start": "16.391"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "than the coupe.", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "21.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It uses a folding hard top that\nfolds in just 17 seconds.", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "23.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s right, you clever people,\nthe opening shot was", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "27.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "actually speeded up.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "30.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The rear screen is electric, and\nyou can lower it with the", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "34.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "roof up to allow some more\nV8 noise into the cabin.", 
            "dur": "3.96", 
            "start": "37.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Apart from a new, smaller\nbonnet badge, the 12C is", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "41.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pretty much as before, and\nthat&#39;s to say far more", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "44.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "interesting up close\nthan in pictures.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "48.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There are some great shapes\nand scoops on this car and", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "50.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "some lovely sculpted details,\nespecially around the rear", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "53.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "tail pipes.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "57.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But just like the 458 Spider,\nwhich is a very similar roof", 
            "dur": "3.886", 
            "start": "63.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "arrangement, those buttresses\ndo look a bit odd from the", 
            "dur": "3.192", 
            "start": "67.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "front three quarter view.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "70.694"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Allowing natural light into the\ncabin makes it look even", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "82.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "better than before.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "85.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If the exterior styling is a\nbit easy [INAUDIBLE], the", 
            "dur": "3.46", 
            "start": "86.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cabin is just what you&#39;d expect\nfrom McLaren, simple,", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "90.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "clever, and with some\nof the coolest clock", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "93.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "faces on any new car.", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "95.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And just to remind those of you\nwho have forgotten, the", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "97.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "12C has a chassis unlike\nany other motor car.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "100.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The dampers are all\nhydraulically connected, which", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "103.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "allows support to be transferred\nto each corner in", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "105.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fractions of a second.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "108.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The test car was running\noptional carbon ceramic disks,", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "110.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the stickier, thready,\ncoarser tires, and", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "113.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lightweight alloy wheels.", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "115.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were at Ascari race resort,\nto only seem sensible to see", 
            "dur": "3.13", 
            "start": "117.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how much damage chopping the\nroof from a 12C has actually", 
            "dur": "3.19", 
            "start": "120.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "caused to the way it drives.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "123.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, children, this is the\nMP4-12C Spider, or as we now", 
            "dur": "4.87", 
            "start": "134.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have to call it, the 12C Spider\nbecause they&#39;re sort of", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "139.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "dropping the MP4 bit.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "141.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re at Ascari circuit,\nwhich is a mecca", 
            "dur": "3.015", 
            "start": "144.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for going very fast.", 
            "dur": "1.315", 
            "start": "147.691"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there&#39;s lots of stuff to\nhit, so we have to treat it", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "149.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with some respect.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "151.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So what are we looking for?", 
            "dur": "0.96", 
            "start": "152.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, I&#39;m not sure actually,\nbecause we know that the car", 
            "dur": "4.805", 
            "start": "153.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is 40 kilograms heavier,\nbut we also know it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "5.535", 
            "start": "158.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "got a carbon top.", 
            "dur": "0.82", 
            "start": "164.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it doesn&#39;t matter that\nthe roof&#39;s been removed.", 
            "dur": "3.456", 
            "start": "164.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That in itself should mean that,\ndynamically, the car is", 
            "dur": "2.984", 
            "start": "168.282"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "very similar.", 
            "dur": "0.942", 
            "start": "171.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Tell you what it is,\nfecking quick.", 
            "dur": "2.892", 
            "start": "172.208"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This has got the upgraded\nmotor in it, 625 PS.", 
            "dur": "5.192", 
            "start": "181.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fuck me, it&#39;s proper fast.", 
            "dur": "4.86", 
            "start": "186.568"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, convertibles should\nnot be this much fun.", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "198.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Convertibles, right, are for\nsissies, but this is a bloody", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "201.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "animal, this thing.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "205.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The performance is\njust barking.", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "207.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can hear the traction\ngoing [INAUDIBLE].", 
            "dur": "3.572", 
            "start": "224.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have to say, in super stiff\nmode, there is something a", 
            "dur": "2.938", 
            "start": "228.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "little bit artificial about the\nway the chassis feels, but", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "231.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "do you know what, it&#39;s\nnot like any other", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "233.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car you get to drive.", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "235.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s what I find so\ninteresting about it.", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "237.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oop, got that all wrong.", 
            "dur": "0.944", 
            "start": "239.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is unlike any other\ncar out there.", 
            "dur": "3.342", 
            "start": "240.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just so flipping capable.", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "253.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Definitely feels quicker than\nthe last one I drove.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "259.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just so clever.", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "272.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t know whether to\nrespect it for doing", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "273.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "everything for me,\nor to resent it.", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "276.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s difficult to decide.", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "279.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What it is is very good.", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "280.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As the tires are getting hotter,\nI&#39;m getting a little", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "283.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bit of understeer.", 
            "dur": "0.98", 
            "start": "284.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll give you that.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "285.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I love that, ba-ba-ba.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "287.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The direction changes on the\ncar are remarkable, and it", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "296.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just, obviously, has no flex\nat all, absolutely no flex.", 
            "dur": "8.63", 
            "start": "300.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If there is a difference between\nSpider and Coupe, I", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "308.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "couldn&#39;t pick it on the track.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "312.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once we&#39;ve done the sensible\nfast stuff, it only", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "313.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "seemed right to prove that the\nSpider somehow skids like it", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "315.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has an LSD when it doesn&#39;t\nhave an LSD.", 
            "dur": "2.936", 
            "start": "318.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But perhaps the biggest surprise\nis on the road, where", 
            "dur": "2.973", 
            "start": "350.123"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the latest gearbox and engine\ncalibration makes the car", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "353.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "smoother and faster.", 
            "dur": "2.095", 
            "start": "355.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, it is just\ncrazy fast.", 
            "dur": "3.365", 
            "start": "357.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is it a good convertible?", 
            "dur": "1.065", 
            "start": "361.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, the hood mechanism is\nexcellent, but I thought the", 
            "dur": "3.615", 
            "start": "362.141"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cabin was quite windy\nat 85 miles an hour.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "365.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "McLaren reckons 80% of 12Cs sold\nwill now be Spiders, and", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "368.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can see why.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "372.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Me, I always prefer a\nroof over my head,", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "374.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so I&#39;d take a Coupe.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "376.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Either way, you get an\noutstanding machine.", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "378.886"
        }
    ], 
